author: Sam Haysom
title: Ed Sheeran reacts to baby that looks exactly like Ed Sheeran
text:
In what may be the year's most hotly anticipated meeting, Ed Sheeran has come face-to-face with a baby who looks almost exactly like Ed Sheeran.
Or rather, he's come face-to-face with a picture of her.
SEE ALSO: Has Ed Sheeran betrayed Taylor Swift and her squad?
Last month, a picture of this baby girl went viral after someone pointed out her similarity to the pop star.
Why does this baby look more like Ed Sheeran than Ed Sheeran does? pic.twitter.com/3I50d7yQlh
‚Äî Tom Davies üåê (@1TD) March 17, 2017
During an interview on Wednesday for ITV's Good Morning Britain , Sheeran was presented with the viral picture by Richard Arnold.
Here's the glorious moment:
"She's not mine," joked Sheeran after looking at the photo. "She's not mine!"
He went on to grin that it was "mad" to see some things go viral.
Truly a special moment.
